#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Disabling all networking (offline mode)\"]]\n"
msgstr ""
"[[!meta title=\"Deshabilitando todas las conexiones (modo offline)\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If you want to work completely offline, you can disable all networking when "
"starting Tails for additional security. Doing so can be useful to work on "
"sensitive documents."
msgstr ""
"Si quieres trabajar completamente offline puedes deshabilitar todas las "
"redes cuando arrancas Tails para tener una seguridad adicional. Puede ser "
"útil para trabajar en documentos delicados."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "To disable all networking:"
msgstr "Para deshabilitar todas las redes:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"When [[<span class=\"application\">Tails "
"Greeter</span>|startup_options#tails_greeter]] appears, in the <span "
"class=\"guilabel\">Welcome to Tails</span> window, click on the <span "
"class=\"button\">Yes</span> button. Then click on the <span "
"class=\"button\">Forward</span> button."
msgstr ""
"Cuando aparece el [[<span class=\"application\">Tails "
"Greeter</span>|startup_options#tails_greeter]], en la ventana de <span class="
"\"guilabel\">Bienvenida de Tails</span>, haz click en el botón <span class=\""
"button\">Sí</span>. Luego haz click en el botón <span class=\"button\""
">Continuar</span>."

#. type: Bullet: '2. '
msgid ""
"In the <span class=\"guilabel\">Network configuration</span> section, select "
"the <span class=\"guilabel\">Disable all networking</span> option."
msgstr ""
"En la sección <span class=\"guilabel\">Configuración de red</span> "
"selecciona la opción <span class=\"guilabel\">Deshablitar todas las "
"redes</span>."
